title: ISic000566. I.Sicily inscription 000566
body:
Facsimile Images

G(aius) Rabonius ((·)) P(ubli) [f(ilio)]
Pom(ptina) ((·)) Flaccus
Licinia ((·)) C(ai) ((·)) f(ilia)
Thoria ((·)) m(onumentum) ((·)) f(ecit)

Apparatus criticus

Text: CIL

English translation

Gaius Rabonius Flaccus, son of Publius. Licinia Thoria, daughter of Caius, built this monument
